{"id":736,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":736,"title":"Isaiah 34","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 34"],[".studySummary",["i","The Second Coming will be a day of vengeance and judgment—The indignation of the Lord will be upon all nations—His sword will fall upon the world."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.1","order":"02.24.034.47743"},["b","1"],"Come near, ye nations, to hear; and hearken, ye people: let the earth hear, and all that is therein; the world, and all things that come forth of it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.2","order":"02.24.034.47744"},["b","2"],"For the indignation of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"upon all nations, and",["i","his"],"fury upon all their armies: he hath utterly destroyed them, he hath delivered them to the slaughter."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.3","order":"02.24.034.47745"},["b","3"],"Their slain also shall be cast out, and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"stink"],"shall come up out of their carcases, and the mountains shall be melted with their blood."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4","order":"02.24.034.47746"},["b","4"],"And all the host of heaven shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"dissolved"],", and the heavens shall be rolled together as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"scroll"],": and all their host shall fall down, as the leaf falleth off from the vine, and as",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"a falling",["i","fig"]],"from the fig tree."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.5","order":"02.24.034.47747"},["b","5"],"For my sword shall be bathed in heaven: behold, it shall come down upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Idumea"],", and upon the people of my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"curse"],", to judgment."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.6","order":"02.24.034.47748"},["b","6"],"The sword of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is filled with blood, it is made fat with fatness,",["i","and"],"with the blood of lambs and goats, with the fat of the kidneys of rams: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sacrifice"],"in Bozrah, and a great slaughter in the land of Idumea."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.7","order":"02.24.034.47749"},["b","7"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"unicorns"],"shall come down with them, and the bullocks with the bulls; and their land shall be soaked with blood, and their dust made fat with fatness."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.8","order":"02.24.034.47750"},["b","8"],"For",["i","it is"],"the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"vengeance"],",",["i","and"],"the year of recompences for the controversy of Zion."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.9","order":"02.24.034.47751"},["b","9"],"And the streams",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"thereof"],"shall be turned into pitch, and the dust thereof into brimstone, and the land thereof shall become burning pitch."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.10","order":"02.24.034.47752"},["b","10"],"It shall not be quenched night nor day; the smoke thereof shall go up for ever: from generation to generation it shall lie waste; none shall pass through it for ever and ever."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11","order":"02.24.034.47753"},["b","11"],"¶But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"cormorant"],"and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"bittern"],"shall possess it; the owl also and the raven shall dwell in it: and he shall stretch out upon it the line of confusion, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"stones of emptiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.12","order":"02.24.034.47754"},["b","12"],"They shall call the nobles thereof to the kingdom, but none",["i","shall be"],"there, and all her princes shall be nothing."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.13","order":"02.24.034.47755"},["b","13"],"And thorns shall come up in her palaces, nettles and brambles in the fortresses thereof: and it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"an habitation of dragons"],",",["i","and"],"a court for owls."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.14","order":"02.24.034.47756"},["b","14"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wild"],"beasts of the desert shall also meet with the wild beasts of the island, and the satyr shall cry to his fellow; the screech owl also shall rest there, and find for herself a place of rest."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.15","order":"02.24.034.47757"},["b","15"],"There shall the great owl make her nest, and lay, and hatch, and gather under her shadow: there shall the vultures also be gathered, every one with her mate."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.16","order":"02.24.034.47758"},["b","16"],"¶Seek ye out of the book of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and read: no one of these shall fail, none shall want her mate: for my mouth it hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"commanded"],", and his spirit it hath gathered them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.17","order":"02.24.034.47759"},["b","17"],"And he hath cast the lot for them, and his hand hath divided it unto them by line: they shall possess it for ever, from generation to generation shall they dwell therein."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.3a","order":"02.24.034.47760"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.20"},"Joel 2:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4a","order":"02.24.034.47762"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.26"},"Ps. 102:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.26"},"Luke 21:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4b","order":"02.24.034.47764"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14"},"Rev. 6:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14a"},["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 6:14 (Rev. 6:14 note",["i","a"],")"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4c","order":"02.24.034.47766"},["b","4c"],["span.small","HEB"],"an unripe fruit."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.5a","order":"02.24.034.47768"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Edom.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.17.7-22"},"Jer. 49:17 (7–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.14.12-14"},"Ezek. 25:14 (12–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12"},"Amos 9:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.18.8,18-19,21"},"Obad. 1:18 (8, 18–19, 21)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.5b","order":"02.24.034.47770"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.6a","order":"02.24.034.47772"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10"},"Jer. 46:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.7a","order":"02.24.034.47774"},["b","7a"],["span.small","JST"],"Isa. 34:7 …",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","reem"]],"… (",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","Reʼem"]],"is Hebrew for “wild ox.”)"],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.8a","order":"02.24.034.47776"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/61.2"},"Isa. 61:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1.1,3"},"Mal. 4:1 (1, 3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.21.20-21"},"3 Ne. 21:21 (20–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.26.25-28"},"D&C 97:26 (25–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.9a","order":"02.24.034.47778"},["b","9a"],["span.small","IE"],"of Edom."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11a","order":"02.24.034.47780"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/2.14"},"Zeph. 2:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11b","order":"02.24.034.47782"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.23"},"Isa. 14:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11c","order":"02.24.034.47784"},["b","11c"],["span.small","HEB"],"plummet."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.13a","order":"02.24.034.47786"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"the resort of jackals."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.14a","order":"02.24.034.47788"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.21"},"Isa. 13:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.16a","order":"02.24.034.47790"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.7.7,18,37-38"},"D&C 1:7 (7, 18, 37–38)"],"."]]}
